<main class="artic-word-main">
    <h2 class="artic-word-heading">ITSM Photo Upload Guidelines</h2>
    <p>When uploading photos or product images in the ITSM system, please follow the guidelines below to ensure a smooth upload process.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>1. User Profile Photo</h3>
    <p>The maximum file size for user profile photos is 20MB. Please ensure that the file size does not exceed this limit to avoid upload failures.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>2. Product Images</h3>
    <p>The maximum file size for product images is 50MB. Please make sure the uploaded files do not exceed this limit.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>3. Recommended Formats</h3>
    <p>It is recommended to upload JPG or PNG image files to ensure proper recognition and display in the system.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>4. Having Trouble Uploading?</h3>
    <p>If you encounter any issues during the upload process or if the upload fails, please contact the IT department for assistance and support.</p>
    <hr />
    <p>Before uploading, please make sure that the image size and format meet the requirements. This will help improve upload efficiency and reduce the likelihood of errors.</p>

</main>
